kmscon-hangul (10.0.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * im_hangul: rename static functions to avoid libhangul namespace collision
    (fixes build on Ubuntu Noble / GCC 13 with K&R-style libhangul headers)

 -- JohnnyB <johnhsb@outlook.kr>  Sun, 08 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0900

kmscon-hangul (10.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream base: kmscon v10.0.0
  * Add generic input method (IM) abstraction layer (kmscon_im_ops vtable)
  * Add Korean (Hangul) input method via libhangul as first IM backend
  * Add --im-engine, --im-params, --grab-im-toggle options
  * Fix freetype fallback font sizing: use y_ppem instead of line height
  * Fix use-after-free SEGV in drm perform_modeset() on VT switch / DPMS wake
  * Update libtsm subproject to v4.5.0 (statically linked)

 -- JohnnyB <johnhsb@outlook.kr>  Thu, 05 Jun 2026 11:00:00 +0900
